messages.title: HURRY! POLLING STATIONS CLOSE AT 10PM
messages.content: Have you planned out when and where you will vote?

keyPolicies.policyTitle: A strong, independent voice for Cambridge

issues.education: Julian has a strong local track record of deliver for our schools and NHS trusts.
issues.health: Julian has a strong local track record of deliver for our schools and NHS trusts.

images.caption: Julian Huppert - Who will put Cambridge first?

leaflet.additionalNotes: It's Julian or the Labour candidate here! Polling turnout has been high all day and this election is close. Recent polls show LAB at 33%, Julian at 32%, CON at 19%. The conservatives say it is so close they are out of the race! A professional lobbyist or a Labour MEP and now a candidate for Labour just sends another suit. Julian Huppert: An exceptional voice.
